hackathon-description-text: IC Hack attempts to bring back the joy of hacking, but with all the benefits of a major Hackathon. Unlike other major Hackathons, we strive to ensure that anything cool - no matter what type of cool - is rewarded in the end. You don't have to use any specific API if you want to succeed at IC Hack.
hackathon-location-google-maps: https://maps.google.com/?q=338-346 Goswell Road, London, United Kingdom
hackathon-description-header: Imperial College London's annual student run hackathon - bring the banter!
